snippet.title: JOLLY Trailer
snippet.description:
A trailer for my new upcoming "FNaF fan game", JOLLY.
Get the demo here:
http://gamejolt.com/games/jolly/165858

Just to clear this out, JOLLY is a "FNaF fan game" and IS NOT affiliated with Scott Cawthon nor "Sister Location"  what so ever.
